wikipedia_page.main: James Ross Turpin (born 18 March 1997) is an English cricketer. Turpin is a right-arm medium bowler and right-handed batsman. He was born in Fowey, Cornwall, England.Turpin made his first-class debut for Cardiff MCCU against Hampshire in April 2016.
